# Cloudflare Tunnel Token (required only if using --profile tunnel)
# Get this from: Cloudflare Dashboard → Zero Trust → Networks → Tunnels → Create tunnel
# 1. Create a tunnel, choose "Docker" connector type
# 2. Set public hostname (e.g., syncspace.yourdomain.com) origin to: http://frontend:80
# 3. Copy the token and paste below
TUNNEL_TOKEN=